<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Frankfurt am Main</head><p>Der Rat dankt für Vermittlung eines Waffenstillstands mit Reinhard II. von Hanau bis Walpurgis und stimmt einem Schiedsgericht mit den Herren von Hanau bei der Frankfurter Fastenmesse zu. Im beigefügten Zettel wird die Zahlung des Botenlohns bestätigt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_400" id="199v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_400_r1l14">Frankfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_400_r1l15"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / vvie Jr ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l16">frewnde <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> geſant habt / cʒü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l17"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Reÿnhart <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü Hanaw / die mit Jm <expan>awſgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l19"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_400_r1l18">ein </ab></add> gütlich ſteen mit vns <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l20">bis auf ſant <expan>walp<ex>ur</ex>gen</expan> tag <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nehſt kumt vnd den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l21">tag allen on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / . Alſo <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſamen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l22">frewntſchaft mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiʒʒe <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> müwe / die Jr <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l23"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> gehabt habt / vnd <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> das in ſo daſ </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l24">das gütlich ſteen die <expan>egen<ex>enante</ex></expan> cʒeit 
<del rend="strikethrough">n </del> mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l25">Hanaw auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Auch als Jr vns ſchreıbt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l27"> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> eins 
<add><ab facs="#facs_400_r1l26"><expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> tags <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> darvmb beÿ ew in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nehſt <expan>cʒükume<ex>n</ex>d<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l28"><expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vaſte<ex>n</ex>meſʒe</expan> / . Dar cʒü mainen wir die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l29">cʒeſchicken / . . wer <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> / daʒ vns daran ıht <expan>hind<ex>er</ex>n</expan> würd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l30">Das <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weiſheit güt cʒeit vor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<add><ab facs="#facs_401_r1l2">
<del rend="strikethrough">Alſo </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_401_line_1576480403960_786">vnd </ab></add> / ob den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw daran iht <expan>hind<ex>er</ex>n</expan> würd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_401_r1l3">daʒ vns das auch cʒeitlıch cʒewiſſen getan würd / </ab></add>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l32">
<add><ab facs="#facs_400_line_1576480601759_920">vnd <expan>bıt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew </ab><ab facs="#facs_400_line_1576480605408_925">daʒ Jr vns </ab><ab facs="#facs_400_line_1576480608129_930">nicht für v̈bel </ab><ab facs="#facs_400_line_1576480611028_935"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet </ab><ab facs="#facs_400_line_1576480613373_940">daʒ wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_400_line_1576480616623_945"><expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> alſlang </ab><ab facs="#facs_400_line_1576480620658_950">bey vns <expan>gehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvan wir Jn nicht ee <expan>gevertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>mocht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> vnd vvo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> / lıeb <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_line_1576480552814_883">dinſte <expan>beweiſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> / Des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> vvir wıllıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l36">vnd <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das cʒü <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>cʒeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l38">in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> priſce / </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><pb facs="#facs_401" id="200r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_401_r1l4">Cedula </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_401_r1l5">Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den lon <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_400" id="199v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frankfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir ewr
                        frewnde <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> gesant habt czü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Reynhart, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü
                        Hanaw, die mit im <expan>awsgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er <add>ein</add> gütlich steen mit uns
                        <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle bis <app><note><q type="date">auf sant
                            <expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>gen</expan> tag</q>01.05.1412</note></app>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        nehst kumt, und den tag allen on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, also
                                <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        ersamen frewntschaft mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizze
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> müwe, die ir
                            <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> gehabt habt und <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        das gütlich steen die <expan>egen<ex>enante</ex></expan> czeit mit
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Auch als ir uns schreibt
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> eins
                            <add><expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> tags
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, darumb bey ew in
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nehst
                            <expan>czükume<ex>n</ex>d<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vaste<ex>n</ex>mesze</expan>, darczü mainen wir die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cze schicken. Wer
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz uns daran iht
                                <expan>hind<ex>er</ex>n</expan> würd, das
                            <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        weisheit güt czeit vor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <add><add>und</add> ob den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw daran iht
                                <expan>hind<ex>er</ex>n</expan> würd, daz uns das auch czeitlich cze
                            wissen getan würd</add>; <add>und <expan>bit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew, daz
                            ir uns nicht für übel <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, daz wir
                                    <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> alslang bey uns
                                <expan>gehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wan wir in nicht ee
                                    <expan>gevertig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>mocht<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>. Und wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb, <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
                        und dinste <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> wir willig
                        und <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das czü <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> Prisce.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab><pb facs="#facs_401" id="200r"/>Cedula <lb/> Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den lon <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
